<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <title>Email Report</title>
    <style>
        body,
        table,
        td {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #0d0d0d;
            /* Full dark background */
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            /* Dark container */
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .logo img {
            width: 180px;
        }

        .content {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .impressions {
            background-color: #2a2a72;
        }

        /* Blue */
        .clicks {
            background-color: #1e5631;
        }

        /* Green */
        .leads {
            background-color: #722a2a;
        }

        /* Red */
        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffd700;
        }

        /* Gold for key data */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #aaaaaa;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .content {
                padding: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td align="center">
                    <table class="container">
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="logo"><img src="https://assets.cdn.filesafe.space/zpjvSoJ3TMkdq8pcj7VJ/media/6499bf999db2c32f4ad9391e.png" alt="SalesGenius Logo"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="content ">
                                    <p>Hello <span class="highlight">{{ $json.property_email_name }}</span>,</p>
                                    <p>I hope you&apos;re doing well. Last week (<span class="highlight">{{ $('Aggregate').item.json["[object Object]"][0].data[0].date_start }} - {{ $('Aggregate').item.json["[object Object]"][0].data[0].date_stop }}</span>), we spent <span class="highlight">$[Total Spend]</span> on Facebook ads and generated <span class="highlight">[Total Leads]</span> leads. That means each lead cost us <span class="highlight">$[CPL]</span> (Cost Per Lead).</p>
                                    <p><strong>How People Moved Through the Funnel:</strong></p><!-- Impressions Section -->
                                    <div class="section impressions">
                                        <p><strong>üëÄ Impressions</strong></p>
                                        <p>Your ads were shown <span class="highlight">[Number of Impressions]</span> times. An impression is counted every time your ad is displayed on someone&rsquo;s screen in their Facebook or Instagram feed, regardless of whether they click or engage with it.</p>
                                    </div><!-- Clicks Section -->
                                    <div class="section clicks">
                                        <p><strong>‚òùÔ∏è Clicks</strong></p>
                                        <p>Out of all the people who saw your ad, <span class="highlight">[Number of Clicks]</span> clicked on it. Each click represents a potential lead who was interested enough to take action.</p>
                                        <p>The <strong>Click-Through Rate (CTR)</strong> was&nbsp;<span class="highlight">[CTR]%</span>. CTR is calculated as (Clicks &divide; Impressions) &times; 100. A higher CTR means more people found your ad engaging and relevant.<br><br>The benchmark we have at SalesGenius for <strong>CTR is 3%</strong>. This means your ad is <span class="highlight"><strong>[Comparison with 3% benchmark, if lower then benchmark, be positive, and say our team is monitoring it].</strong></span></p>
                                    </div><!-- Leads Section -->
                                    <div class="section leads">
                                        <p><strong>üë• Leads</strong></p>
                                        <p>From those clicks, we ended up with <span class="highlight">[Total Leads]</span> leads. Leads are the most valuable part of our funnel since they show real potential customers.</p>
                                        <p>The <strong>Cost Per Lead (CPL)</strong> was <span class="highlight">$[CPL]</span>. CPL is calculated as <strong>(Total Spend &divide; Total Leads)</strong>. This means we spent&nbsp;<strong>$[CPL] for each new lead</strong> who showed interest in your offer.&nbsp;<br><br>The benchmark we have at SalesGenius for <strong>CPL is $20</strong>. This means your ad is <span class="highlight"><strong>[Comparison with $20 CPL benchmark, if lower then benchmark, be positive, and say our team is monitoring it].</strong></span></p>
                                    </div><!-- Best Performing Day -->
                                    <p><strong>üåü Best Performing Day</strong></p>
                                    <p>Our best day was <span class="highlight">[Best Day/Date]</span>, with <span class="highlight">[Best Day Leads]</span> leads and a Cost Per Lead of <span class="highlight">$[Best Day CPL]</span>. This day gave us the best value for our spend.</p>
                                    <p>Thank you for reading! If you have any questions, feel free to reach out.</p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="footer">
                                    <p>Best regards,</p>
                                    <p><strong>The SalesGenius Team</strong></p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</body>

</html>



